'''真蝦下目'''（學名：{{lang|la|Caridea}}），是[[抱卵亞目|抱卵亞目]]的其中一個下目<ref name="Grave">{{cite journal |journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2009 |volume=Suppl. 21 |pages=1–109 |title=A classification of living and fossil genera of decapod crustaceans |author=Sammy De Grave, N. Dean Pentcheff, Shane T. Ahyong ''et al.'' |url=http://digitalcommons.kent.edu/geolpubs/96/ |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2019-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224035248/https://digitalcommons.kent.edu/geolpubs/96/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="blueanimalbio">{{cite book |chapter=软甲纲（Malacostraca） |chapter-url=http://www.blueanimalbio.com/bugs/ruanjia/index.htm |title=蓝色动物学 |url=http://www.blueanimalbio.com/ |access-date=2018-06-15 |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2011-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110128174951/http://www.blueanimalbio.com/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。這類動物在[[淡水|淡水]]和[[海水|海水]]環境中都有分佈。人們日常所知的[[蝦|蝦]]多指這類動物。

==科學分類==
