*{{le|Anchialocarididae}}科 {{small|Mejía-Ortíz, Yañez & López-Mejía, 2017}}：新建立
*[[匙指蝦總科|匙指蝦總科]] Atyoidea {{small|De Haan, 1849 [in De Haan, 1833-1850]}}
*{{le|臂蝦總科|Bresilioidea}} Bresilioidea {{small|Calman, 1896}}
*{{le|彎背蝦總科|Campylonotoidea}} Campylonotoidea {{small|Sollaud, 1913}}
*{{le|褐蝦總科|Crangonoidea}} Crangonoidea {{small|Haworth, 1825}}
*{{le|線足蝦總科|Nematocarcinoidea}} Nematocarcinoidea {{small|Smith, 1884}}
*{{le|刺蝦總科|Oplophoroidea}} Oplophoroidea {{small|Dana, 1852}}
*[[長臂蝦總科|長臂蝦總科]] Palaemonoidea {{small|Rafinesque, 1815}}
*[[長額蝦總科|長額蝦總科]] Pandaloidea {{small|Haworth, 1825}}
*[[玻璃蝦總科|玻璃蝦總科]] Pasiphaeoidea {{small|Dana, 1852}}
*{{le|寬背蝦總科|Physetocaridoidea}} Physetocaridoidea {{small|Chace, 1940}}
*{{le|異指蝦總科|Processoidea}} Processoidea {{small|Ortmann, 1896}}
*{{le|剪足蝦總科|Psalidopodoidea}} Psalidopodoidea {{small|Wood-Mason [in Wood-Mason & Alcock, 1892]}}
*{{le|棒指蝦總科|Stylodactyloidea}} Stylodactyloidea {{small|Spence Bate, 1888}}
;異名
